codex
I’ve narrowed the change to a deterministic section-range parser that recognizes `X to Y` / `through` ranges and emits typed range + endpoint slots while preserving existing component slots. I’m patching this in both decompiler and codec so slot text maps and F-logic triples stay aligned.
